sql:
SELECT
    q.quarter, q.commit_upside, m.metric_value, l.linearity_score, f.funnel_stage
FROM cisco_stage_app.qtd_commit_upside AS q
    INNER
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.metrics AS m
    ON q.quarter = m.quarter
    INNER
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.linearity_metrics AS l
    ON q.quarter = l.quarter
    INNER
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.funnel_metrics AS f
    ON q.quarter = f.quarter
